<VirtualHost *:443>

					DocumentRoot /var/www/clients/client1/web1/web
			
		ServerName oktodigital.com
		ServerAlias www.oktodigital.com 
    ServerAlias www.okto.digital okto.digital
		ServerAdmin webmaster@oktodigital.com

		ErrorLog /var/log/ispconfig/httpd/oktodigital.com/error.log


		<IfModule mod_ssl.c>
		SSLEngine on
		SSLProtocol All -SSLv2 -SSLv3
		# SSLCipherSuite          ECDHE-ECDSA-CHACHA20-POLY1305:ECDHE-RSA-CHACHA20-POLY1305:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:ECDHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384:ECDHE-RSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384:DHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:DHE-RSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES128-SHA256:ECDHE-RSA-AES128-SHA256:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES128-SHA:ECDHE-RSA-AES256-SHA384:ECDHE-RSA-AES128-SHA:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES256-SHA384:ECDHE-ECDSA-AES256-SHA:ECDHE-RSA-AES256-SHA:DHE-RSA-AES128-SHA256:DHE-RSA-AES128-SHA:DHE-RSA-AES256-SHA256:DHE-RSA-AES256-SHA:ECDHE-ECDSA-DES-CBC3-SHA:ECDHE-RSA-DES-CBC3-SHA:EDH-RSA-DES-CBC3-SHA:AES128-GCM-SHA256:AES256-GCM-SHA384:AES128-SHA256:AES256-SHA256:AES128-SHA:AES256-SHA:DES-CBC3-SHA:!DSS
		SSLHonorCipherOrder     on
		# <IfModule mod_headers.c>
		# Header always add Strict-Transport-Security "max-age=15768000"
		# </IfModule>
		SSLCertificateFile /var/www/clients/client1/web1/ssl/oktodigital.com.crt
		SSLCertificateKeyFile /var/www/clients/client1/web1/ssl/oktodigital.com.key
				SSLCertificateChainFile /var/www/clients/client1/web1/ssl/oktodigital.com.bundle
						SSLUseStapling on
		SSLStaplingResponderTimeout 5
		SSLStaplingReturnResponderErrors off
				</IfModule>

		<Directory /var/www/oktodigital.com/web>
				# Clear PHP settings of this website
				<FilesMatch ".+\.ph(p[345]?|t|tml)$">
						SetHandler None
				</FilesMatch>
				Options +FollowSymLinks
				AllowOverride All
								Require all granted
						</Directory>
		<Directory /var/www/clients/client1/web1/web>
				# Clear PHP settings of this website
				<FilesMatch ".+\.ph(p[345]?|t|tml)$">
						SetHandler None
				</FilesMatch>
				Options +FollowSymLinks
				AllowOverride All
								Require all granted
						</Directory>




		# suexec enabled
		<IfModule mod_suexec.c>
			SuexecUserGroup web1 client1
		</IfModule>
		<IfModule mod_fastcgi.c>
				<Directory /var/www/clients/client1/web1/cgi-bin>
										Require all granted
								    </Directory>
				<Directory /var/www/oktodigital.com/web>
					<FilesMatch "\.php[345]?$">
						SetHandler php5-fcgi
					</FilesMatch>
				</Directory>
				<Directory /var/www/clients/client1/web1/web>
					<FilesMatch "\.php[345]?$">
						SetHandler php5-fcgi
					</FilesMatch>
				</Directory>
                Action php5-fcgi /php5-fcgi virtual
				Alias /php5-fcgi /var/www/clients/client1/web1/cgi-bin/php5-fcgi-*-443-oktodigital.com
                FastCgiExternalServer /var/www/clients/client1/web1/cgi-bin/php5-fcgi-*-443-oktodigital.com -idle-timeout 300 -host 127.0.0.1:9010 -pass-header Authorization             
		</IfModule>
		<IfModule mod_proxy_fcgi.c>
			#ProxyPassMatch ^/(.*\.php[345]?(/.*)?)$ fcgi://127.0.0.1:9010/var/www/clients/client1/web1/web/$1
			<Directory /var/www/clients/client1/web1/web>
				<FilesMatch "\.php[345]?$">
						SetHandler "proxy:fcgi://127.0.0.1:9010"
				</FilesMatch>
			</Directory>
			</IfModule>


		RewriteEngine on
		RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} ^/\.well-known/acme-challenge/
		RewriteRule ^ - [END]
		RewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} ^oktodigital\.com$ [NC]
				RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://www.oktodigital.com$1 [R=301,NE,L]
		RewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST}   ^okto\.digital$ [NC]
				
		RewriteRule   ^/(.*)$ https://www.oktodigital.com/$1  [R=301,L]
	
		RewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST}   ^www\.okto\.digital$ [NC]
				
		RewriteRule   ^/(.*)$ https://www.oktodigital.com/$1  [R=301,L]
	

		# add support for apache mpm_itk
		<IfModule mpm_itk_module>
			AssignUserId web1 client1
		</IfModule>

		<IfModule mod_dav_fs.c>
		# Do not execute PHP files in webdav directory
			<Directory /var/www/clients/client1/web1/webdav>
				<ifModule mod_security2.c>
					SecRuleRemoveById 960015
					SecRuleRemoveById 960032
				</ifModule>
				<FilesMatch "\.ph(p3?|tml)$">
					SetHandler None
				</FilesMatch>
			</Directory>
			DavLockDB /var/www/clients/client1/web1/tmp/DavLock
			# DO NOT REMOVE THE COMMENTS!
			# IF YOU REMOVE THEM, WEBDAV WILL NOT WORK ANYMORE!
      # WEBDAV BEGIN
			# WEBDAV END
		</IfModule>

RewriteEngine On
RewriteCond %{HTTPS} off
RewriteRule (.*) https://%{HTTP_HOST}%{REQUEST_URI}

</VirtualHost>

<IfModule mod_ssl.c>
        SSLStaplingCache shmcb:/var/run/ocsp(128000)
</IfModule>
